# V2 stores one generated key id per profile.
# The CLI creates these automatically, for example:
# CCKEY_<PROVIDER>_<PROFILE>_<RANDOM_ID>=
#
# Use `cc-manage key list` to see generated ids and profile ownership.
# Mistral Vibe profiles default to MISTRAL_VIBE_API_KEY-derived generated ids.
# Codestral profiles default to CODESTRAL_API_KEY-derived generated ids.
# OpenCode Zen profiles default to OPENCODE_API_KEY-derived generated ids.
